        content: {
          intro: `Phoenix homeowners leave thousands of dollars in HVAC rebates unclaimed every year. APS and SRP both run incentive programs for energy-efficient heating and cooling equipment, and those rebates stack with the federal 25C tax credit. This is a current guide to what's available from both utilities and how to claim it.`,
